<materialsCitation ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3806466321" pageId="6" pageNumber="463">
type locality unknown. Restricted by P. Hershkovitz in 1963 to the Lago do 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Lonnberg" authorityYear="1939" box="[1982,2099,912,941]" class="Mammalia" family="Pitheciidae" genus="Callicebus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Primates" pageId="6" pageNumber="463" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="baptista">Baptista</taxonomicName>
